thing new, something I wasn't aware of yesterday. 
So here's something from the semi-popular school kid who found utmost happiness in being a semi loner - there isn't a defined checklist to define one of being cool or uncool. There‚Äôs just a conflict of who our teenage self wanted us to be and who we truly are. üß°
.
.
